 276:src/engine.cpp ****         // Amp decay-to-sustain: s_decay rides 1 â†’ sustain over decay_ms while the
 277:src/engine.cpp ****         // note is gated (stays pinned at 1 when decay_ms == 0, i.e. every other
 278:src/engine.cpp ****         // voice). It scales the gated target so the note plucks down to `sustain`.
